Business Brief -- Sunshine Mining Co.:
   Firm, Metals Unit Extend
   Exchange Offer to Feb. 28
Under the offer and reorganization plan, holders of $1,000
face amount of Sunshine Precious Metals' silver-indexed bonds
would receive $200 of Sunshine Mining common stock and $800
face amount of new 8% silver-indexed bonds of Sunshine
Precious Metals. The unit has eight issues outstanding of the
silver-indexed bonds with a total face value of $71.5
million.
   Sunshine Mining, which is based in Dallas, said about $34
million of the bonds have been tendered under the exchange
offer. The company also said holders of $28 million face
value of bonds have voted in favor of the reorganization
plan, representing 71% of the bonds voted so far.